&lt;h1 id="what-business-can-learn-from-open-source"&gt;What Business Can Learn from Open Source&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;August 2005&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;(This essay is derived from a talk at Oscon 2005.)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lately companies have been paying more attention to open source. Ten years ago there seemed a real danger Microsoft would extend its monopoly to servers. It seems safe to say now that open source has prevented that. A recent survey found 52% of companies are replacing Windows servers with Linux servers. [1]&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>